    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has served as a dependable daily driver. The engine and transmission are in good working order, though the exterior shows its age with a few minor door dings and some thinning of the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear from regular use, and all major electronics are functional. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for reliable transportation without the premium price of a showroom-quality model.",
