    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to enjoy the road in this wonderful find! This vehicle is in truly good condition, having been consistently well-maintained to provide a smooth and reliable driving experience. While it shows some light, expected signs of previous love, it remains a fantastic, high-quality choice for anyone seeking a dependable and stylish ride!",
